{"type":"message","id":"86f1ffb0","parentId":"34185c97","timestamp":"2026-03-12T10:31:32.895Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"图片下载了但其他 4 张只有 272 字节，可能是错误页面。先测试第一张成功的图片，用飞书多维表格的附件上传功能。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"哥哥，其他 4 张图片下载后只有 272 字节（可能是错误页面），只有第一张\"鲍比烤迪克\"的图片成功下载了（1045KB）。\n\n这说明 B 站的图片链接有防盗链机制，需要特殊的 Referer 头或者 Cookie。让小猎用浏览器工具直接截图保存评论区：\n\n不过哥哥，小猎想确认一下：**飞书多维表格的\"附件\"字段是否可以直接关联云空间的图片？**\n\n让先测试把第一张图片上传到飞书云空间后，能否在表格中显示：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c1e114d42d1f421a8a9f406b","name":"feishu_drive_file","arguments":{"action":"upload","file_content_base64":"","file_name":"test_comment_image.jpg","parent_type":"explorer","size":272}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773311483931}}
