{"type":"message","id":"fd43126b","parentId":"7c091fe2","timestamp":"2026-03-12T10:36:49.534Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，截图保存了。现在小猎需要裁剪出 5 条带图片的评论区域。让我使用 ImageMagick 来裁剪图片：\n\n1. zk 闪光 - \"报错怎么解决\"\n2. 百里清笙 - \"求解，第一天玩的好好的今天玩一会就跳这个\"\n3. 心比铁还硬的男人 - \"这是怎么回事有没有大佬帮忙解决一下\"\n4. 指间旋律 sj - \"有没有人遇到这种的？？\"\n5. 威先生--\"我为啥是这样的用了修改器后，删掉就正常\"\n\n让我先裁剪出第一条评论（zk 闪光）：\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ 截图完成！现在小猎裁剪出 5 条带图片的评论区域，然后分别上传到飞书：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_581d24cd0a0246c4b784a4d5","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /tmp/bilibili_images && cp /Users/wh1ko/.openclaw/media/browser/327e7ec3-1819-4eb1-ac43-02e2bd7aab04.jpg full_comment.jpg && convert full_comment.jpg -crop 1200x400+50+1500 zk_comment1.jpg && convert full_comment.jpg -crop 1200x400+50+1900 zk_comment2.jpg && convert full_comment.jpg -crop 1200x400+50+2300 zk_comment3.jpg && convert full_comment.jpg -crop 1200x400+50+2700 zk_comment4.jpg && convert full_comment.jpg -crop 1200x400+50+3100 zk_comment5.jpg && ls -la *.jpg","timeout":30}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773311782727}}
