{"type":"message","id":"38153cf3","parentId":"9847b037","timestamp":"2026-03-12T12:12:43.620Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户指出只有第一张图片正确，后面 4 张都是纯黑图片。从浏览器快照可以看到评论区的结构，每条评论都有 img 元素显示图片。问题出在裁剪坐标计算错误，需要重新截图并调整裁剪位置。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"小猎看到问题了！😅 裁剪区域计算错误，导致后面 4 张裁剪到了空白区域。\n\n从哥哥的截图可以看到：\n- ✅ 百里清笙的评论有图片（游戏报错截图）\n- ✅ 真的已经燃尽了的评论有图片（黑色背景的报错窗口）\n\n让小猎重新用正确的方法 - 先滚动到评论区，然后对每条评论单独截图：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7ff21531ff314c939ec1578d","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"navigate","targetId":"C9968152C24BF7706CAD7BE79DC0E37F","url":"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV15QAUzXEtP/?spm_id_from=333.788.comment.all.click"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773317534435}}
